sub_title: Russian as a Foreign Language Teacher
summary:
Life-long learner, flexible and open-minded IB educator with a Master of Education (M.Ed.) focused in International Teaching.
- Certified MYP IB teacher, certified teacher of Russian as a foreign language.
- International-minded, lived and worked in Russia, Netherlands and Turkey.
- With international experience as a university student in the Netherlands and as a college teacher in the Netherlands.
